title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 8/30 - 12 Reasons, Gabe Henderson
description: With the season opener 12 days away, PA & Nordo give you 12 reasons why the Vikings will beat the Packers week 1.  Plus, Gabe Henderson of the Vikings Entertainment Network joins the show to discuss all the latest with the purple & gold!
